    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Here Comes The Tune</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Well here comes the tune in this curing full moon </l>
          <l>Drawing fields of pasture before our eyes </l>
          <l>And as the empty night comes</l>
          <l>You can lean on me love ’til the dawn </l>
          <l>For here comes the tune </l>
          <l>Looking back I can see how the light is guiding me </l>
          <l>Now that I have you here by my side </l>
          <l>And as the empty night comes</l>
          <l>We’ll be carried away to the sound </l>
          <l>Of a beautiful tune</l>
          <l>That’s rocking our minds </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>And I’m wishing to God you will see</l>
          <l>All the innocence that once lived in me </l>
          <l>But it was lost and forgotten my name</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
